# Each corpus lives in its own directory here. The programs it holds
# are fetched or copied from their own source and are not committed --
# they belong to others, or are generated (see README.md). The small
# per-corpus prelude that lets a corpus run (e.g. ghostscript/prelude)
# is committed; a large generated one (bwipp/prelude, the barcode
# resource) is not.
*/*.ps
*/*.eps
*/*.ppm
*/*.pbm
*/*.pgm
*/*.png
bwipp/prelude
.work/
